title: The Face Thailand
overview: The Face is a Thai reality television modelling competition series aired on Channel 3 In Thailand. Auditions for the show began on 23 August 2014. Aspiring contestants were required to be between the ages of 12 and 27, and meet a minimum height requirement of 165 cm (5 ft 5 in). The series began to air on television on 4 October 2014.
